               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     3ra-73vb)&#xD; I-1) Homily by Timothy (Dämatiwos), Patriarch of Alexandria for
                     the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 3ra-9ra)&#xD; I-2) Homily by an anonymous author for
                     Tāḫśāś (fols. 9ra-14va)&#xD; I-3) Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of
                     Cyprus] for Ṭǝrr (fols. 14va-23ra)&#xD; I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for
                     Yakkātit (fols. 23ra-25vb)&#xD; I-5) Homily by [Severus] Patriarch of Antiochia
                     for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 25vb-39va)&#xD; I-6) Homily by [Metropolitan
                     Yoḥannǝs] the Orthodox for Miyāzyā (fols. 39va-43va)&#xD; I-7) Homily by
                     Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Ethiopia for Gǝnbot (fols. 43va-45ra)&#xD; I-8)
                     Homily by [Yoḥannǝs], Metropolitan of ʾAksum [for Sane] (fols. 45ra-50va)&#xD;
                     I-9) Homily [by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] for Ḥamle (fols. 50va-54rb)&#xD; I-10)
                     Homily by an anonymous author for Naḥāse (fols. 54rb-56vb)&#xD; I-11) Homily by
                     an anonymous author for Maskaram (fols. 56vb-58vb)&#xD; I-12) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 58vb-62rb)&#xD; I-13) Miracles of St
                     Michael: 12 miracles (fols. 62ra-73vb)&#xD; - Introduction (fol. 62ra-rb)&#xD;
                     II) Dǝrsāna Gabrǝʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Gabriel (fols.
                     75ra-99vb)&#xD; II-1) Homily (for the 19th of Tāḫśāś) (fols. 75ra-83vb)&#xD;
                     II-2) Miracles of St Gabriel: 13 miracles (fols. 84ra-99vb), incomplete&#xD;
                     III) Malkǝʾa Gabrǝʾel "Image of Gabriel" (fols. 101ra-102rb)&#xD; &#xD;
                     Additiones 1-2.</summary>
